name: S.O.C.S. (Symptoms Of Culture Shock) Still Kicking Tee
description: Not only paying homage to one of my artistic heroes but the message "still kicking' is synonymous with being a creative. Branching out on your own artistic merit and making ends meet takes courage that some will never understand. My brand...my name...my art is all about that. Putting yourself out there and no matter the failures and the no's you keep pushing. Because you know success isn't easy. You have to wake up everyday still kicking. Perseverance is key. Only the strong survive. This is a unisex print. Click your size and the design will be black on white tee. New colorways coming soon.
